snippet.title: Yuri Game Jam 2023: DRMWRLDGRL - Trailer
snippet.description:
DRMWRLDGRL Out Now!!!!!!!!!!

GIRLXGIRL, DON'T LIKE, DON'T PLAY!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
Emmett is a regular girl, she lives a regular life, and doesn't have many complaints.
Nova is a dream imp made from ash and bone.
One day they meet.

2K Words, 9 Dreams, 30+ cgs.
Submission to Yuri Game Jam 2023!!!

Game Link: https://m-9.itch.io/drmwrldgrl
M9 Itch.io Page: https://m-9.itch.io/
M9 Twitter Page: https://twitter.com/ermm_9
CallingGestalt Twitter Page: https://twitter.com/CallingGestalt
